{"tid":596524,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"遇過同學對老師做啲咩黐線野？","createTime":"2018-03-17T17:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T03:08:13.000Z","uid":147789,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"800deb71c6c7e4be0e9ea9b60be591220e97d053","tid":596524,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T17:26:13.000Z","msg":"中學有個似係自閉+異常樣衰嘅女同學<br />\n大概係咁嘅樣：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/012525_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F012525_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=817c05de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上英文堂嗰陣佢成日好積極咁搏表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係個老師比較鍾意另一個同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢不滿個老師偏心<br />\n有朝佢擺咗支入面充滿黃色液體嘅維他膠樽落個老師嘅教員室枱到<br />\n個老師後尾講返話支野攞上手重係暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到依家都覺得好黐線<br />\n勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ec1b2b9d23f3cb85d46b34e5249d9f9dd5da2f","tid":596524,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T03:08:13.000Z","msg":"冇人返過學？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}